# Hand-edited input for LOCAL / editable dependencies that cannot live in
# pyproject.toml's [project.dependencies] (not published to PyPI).
#
# All PyPI dependencies are declared in pyproject.toml [project.dependencies].
# This file only adds the local editable sibling package.
#
# Regenerate the pinned lock (requirements.txt) with:
#   pip-compile pyproject.toml requirements.in -o requirements.txt
-e ../common-av-codebase
